Package: deqalcrit
Title: Implementation of Oregon DEQ's Aluminum Criteria Procedures 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Travis",
           family = "Pritchard",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "travis.pritchard@deq.state.or.us",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package provides tools needed to implement Oregon DEQ's aluminum criteria procudeures. The tools include a reworked version of EPA's aluminum criteria calculator and various tools to query needed data from the AWQMS database. 
